'''Avazbek Alisher oʻgʻli Ulmasaliev''' (born 27 March 2000) is an Uzbekistani professional footballer who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[FC AGMK|AGMK]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==Club career==
Ulmasaliev is a graduate of the Neftchi Children's Football Academy. He began his professional career in the 2016 season as part of the youth team of [[FC Neftchi Fergana|Neftchi Fergana]] and signed his first professional contract with the Fergana team in the 2017 season.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://stadion.uz/news/detail/134181 |title="Нефтчи" ёшлари "Цементчи"ни мағлуб этди |date=18 July 2016 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=20 January 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250120142052/https://stadion.uz/news/detail/134181 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://stadion.uz/news/detail/172612 |title="Нефтчи" янги футболчиларни таништирди |date=3 August 2017 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=20 January 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250120142025/https://stadion.uz/news/detail/172612 |url-status=live }}</ref> Ulmasaliev became one of the main players in his first season with the club and scored 1 goal in 9 games.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://stadion.uz/news/detail/182388 |title=Музаффаров ёш жамоадошига омад тилади |date=21 November 2017 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=24 December 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231224192026/https://stadion.uz/news/detail/182388 |url-status=live }}</ref> In the 2018 season, he participated in 15 games and scored his only goal of the season in a match against [[FC Nasaf|Nasaf]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://stadion.uz/news/detail/210354 |title=Суперлига: "Пахтакор"да ғалаба, Насаф» эса сафарда мағлуб бўлди |date=22 September 2018 |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=20 January 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250120142035/https://stadion.uz/news/detail/210354 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/superliga-2018-eng-yosh-va-eng-faxriy-futbolchilar-haqida |title=Суперлига-2018. Энг ёш ва энг фахрий футболчилар ҳақида |date=7 December 2018}}</ref>

At the end of the season, due to Neftchi being relegated to the [[Uzbekistan Pro League]], Ulmasaliev changed clubs and signed a contract with [[PFC Lokomotiv Tashkent|Lokomotiv Tashkent]] in 2019.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/lokomotiv-yangi-futbolchilarni-tanishtirdi-foto-3 |title="Локомотив" янги футболчиларни таништирди ФОТО |date=28 February 2019 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=24 December 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231224190340/https://championat.asia/uz/news/lokomotiv-yangi-futbolchilarni-tanishtirdi-foto-3 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/lokomotiv-yangi-yil-oldidan-yana-bir-transferga-qol-urdi |title="Локомотив" янги йил олдидан яна бир трансферга қўл урди |date=31 December 2018|language=uz}}</ref> His first trophy with his new team was the [[2019 Uzbekistan Super Cup|Uzbekistan Super Cup]]. He played for the Railroaders for two seasons.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/kecha-qorqinchli-jarohat-olgan-neftchi-futbolchisi-qachon-safga-qaytadi-video-18 |title=Кеча қўрқинчли жароҳат олган "Нефтчи" футболчиси қачон сафга қайтади? ВИДЕО (+18) |date=23 September 2018|language=uz}}</ref>

Ulmasaliev moved to another Tashkent team in the 2021 season, in which he was loaned to [[FC Bunyodkor|Bunyodkor]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://stadion.uz/news/detail/278842 |title="Бунёдкор" ўз олдига чемпионликни мақсад қилиб қўймоқда |date=9 March 2021 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=24 December 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231224192604/https://stadion.uz/news/detail/278842 |url-status=live }}</ref> During one season at Bunyodkor, he became one of the team's most reliable players. Before the 2022 season, Ulmasaliev signed a contract with [[Pakhtakor FC|Pakhtakor]],<ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/312999 |title=Расмий хабар: Авазбек Ўлмасалиев "Пахтакор" футболчисига айланди |date=11 January 2022 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=24 December 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231224190428/https://championat.asia/uz/news/312999 |url-status=live }}</ref> but later returned to the Bunyodkor a month later due to disagreements over the terms of the contract.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/avazbek-olmasalievning-shov-shuvli-transferi-u-nima-sababdan-bunyodkorga-qaytganini-malum-qildi |title=Авазбек Ўлмасалиевнинг шов-шувли трансфери: у нима сабабдан "Бунёдкор"га қайтганини маълум қилди |date=1 February 2022 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=20 January 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250120142037/https://championat.asia/uz/news/avazbek-olmasalievning-shov-shuvli-transferi-u-nima-sababdan-bunyodkorga-qaytganini-malum-qildi |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/11-yanvar-kuni-paxtakor-bilan-shartnoma-imzolagan-avazbek-olmasaliev-kutilmaganda-bunyodkor-azosiga-aylandi |title=Расман: 11 январь куни "Пахтакор" билан шартнома имзолаган Авазбек Ўлмасалиев кутилмаганда "Бунёдкор" аъзосига айланди |date=1 February 2022|language=uz}}</ref> He started the 2022 season with Bunyodkor,<ref>{{cite web |url=https://stadion.uz/news/detail/314276 |title="Бунёдкор" янги харидни амалга оширди (фото) |date=1 February 2022 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=24 December 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231224192409/https://stadion.uz/news/detail/314276 |url-status=live }}</ref> scored 1 goal in 48 matches in the Uzbekistan Super League for two seasons, and was promoted to the club captain in the 2023 season.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/biz-hali-kop-jamoalarga-bosh-ogriq-bolamiz-bunyodkorni-sardori-endi-avazbek-olmasaliev |title="Биз ҳали кўп жамоаларга бош оғриқ бўламиз" — "Бунёдкор"нинг янги сардори |date=9 September 2023 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=20 January 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250120142026/https://championat.asia/uz/news/biz-hali-kop-jamoalarga-bosh-ogriq-bolamiz-bunyodkorni-sardori-endi-avazbek-olmasaliev |url-status=live }}</ref> At the end of the 2023 season, his contract with Bunyodkor expired and he left the club as a free agent.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://stadion.uz/news/detail/418515 |title=Авазбек Ўлмасалиев эркин агентга айланди |date=23 December 2023 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=24 December 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231224192013/https://stadion.uz/news/detail/418515 |url-status=live }}</ref>

On 9 January 2024, Ulmasaliev signed a two-year contract with [[FC AGMK|AGMK]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://championat.asia/uz/news/360287?utm_source=telegram&utm_medium=championatasia |title=Расман: ОКМК "Бунёдкор" сардори билан шартнома имзолаганини эълон қилди |date=9 January 2024 |language=uz |access-date=16 May 2026 |archive-date=20 January 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250120142201/https://championat.asia/uz/news/360287?utm_source=telegram&utm_medium=championatasia |url-status=live }}</ref>

==International career==
Ulmasaliev was included in Uzbekistan's squad which won the [[2025 CAFA Nations Cup]].<ref>{{cite web | title=Instagram - Uzbekistan squad | url=https://www.instagram.com/cafassociation/p/DN2475A2H4Y/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Uzbekistan defeats Iran to win 2025 CAFA Nations Cup |url=https://kun.uz/en/news/2025/09/09/uzbekistan-defeats-iran-to-win-cafa-2025-cup |access-date=9 September 2025 |work=KUN.uz |date=9 September 2025 }}</ref>

On 5 May 2026, Ulmasaliev was named to Uzbekistan's 40-man preliminary squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]] and named to the final squad was 2 June.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.facebook.com/UzbekistanFA/posts/pfbid0JohE1JdZ8B9mWiKN56GHDEUV9cN2mFM5LmxEsDakReXy7JsMkbRLLxpT4ptENozZl |title=Training Camp May 6–26: Uzbekistan Squad |publisher=[[Uzbekistan Football Association]] |via=[[Facebook]] |date=May 5, 2026 |access-date=May 5, 2026 |language=uz, en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Khusanov named in Uzbekistan's World Cup squad|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/c5yenm7xllyo|website=BBC.com|date=June 2, 2026|access-date=June 2, 2026|archive-date=June 2, 2026|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20260602151432/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/articles/c5yenm7xllyo|url-status=live}}</ref>

